			<div><strong>Where to find bloodstones</strong><br />&nbsp;</div>
		
		
		
		<div>I humbly beg your pardon for asking such a newbie question, but what area can I hunt to find MOB's that drop bloodstones?  I am currently level 20 and looking forward to new spells and a new symbol in the future and thought I would try to kill two birds with one stone - gain exp and bloodstones in the same area.  <br />
<br />
Thank you for your help.</div>
